### Variables
### GET exam by code (HEM001 - performable)
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam-catalog/HEM001

### GET exam by code (ONC001 - non-performable, routing signal)
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam-catalog/ONC001

### GET exam by code (GEN001 - non-performable)
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam-catalog/GEN001

### GET non-existent exam (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam-catalog/nonexistent-code

### GET all exams
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam-catalog

### GET exam catalog filtered — only routable (can_perform=false)
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam-catalog?can_perform=false

### GET exam catalog filtered — only performable (can_perform=true)
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam-catalog?can_perform=true
